Taube Records launches with Turbosh's electrifying ‚Call Me’ EP. In the pulsating heart of electronic music's ever-evolving landscape, Taube Records emerges with its inaugural release - an energizing EP from the dynamic duo, Turbosh. This EP heralds a new era of high-energy trance, ravy uplifts, technoid resonance, and pop influences, transcending traditional genres. The mastery of Turbosh in weaving emotional electronic tapestries is evident in each of the four tracks, where each composition becomes a unique exploration, an audacious dance between euphoria and intensity. The collaboration with label founder Taube himself adds an extra layer of significance, blending visionary artistry with personal passion. More than just a collection of tracks, this EP is a manifesto of Taube Records' ethos - to build a global community of artists, shatter the confines of electronic music, and embark on uncharted sonic territories.

We proudly present: Synthetic Love’s Various Artist Vol. 2 💗

Dive into seven unique tracks full of pumping Trance who don’t hesitate to dip in oldschool roots. The EP is showcasting both, the sound of Synthetic Love but especially of seven highly talented producers, who you will already know - and if you don’t, you definitely will after the first listen. We are so happy to have our artists producing gems we can proudly share with you. Thank all of you from the bottom of our heart!

